{
  "stem": "22582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- we met him in a hospital, so somehow he survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what happened with the Czech guy, if they-- if he brought SS people or not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we were scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somehow, we were-- we were always going further, further, and farther.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not to-- to help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they help us when they found us that we were there, and they gave us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's just to go away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't want nothing to do with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were scared themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to help, I don't think, no, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have any occasion, because we were always on the run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't know the intention of this Polish guy who was there, because I think that he brought some Germans, because we saw it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] he brought somebody there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we didn't stay long enough to-- to-- to know who it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally, we-- we went to a place, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We took off the jackets, because not to be recognized as the-- that we were prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember, we went to eat something somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a guy was looking at us, and they were looking at-- And I thought that-- you know, at the time, all the guards were changing in civilian suits.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were always holding something under their arm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I-- somehow we recognized that he must have been a guard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember, there was a public place where they ate during.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we saw them, so we went out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he went after us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so he shot something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he-- you know, we thought he didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He knew it's end of the world.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
